text: I need a snack. What is there?
I need something else. I'm still hungry.
Aren't you supposed to be on a diet?
Give me it... uh, where are we?
A fishing rod? I don't want to catch my own food.
Great, exactly what I wanted, a smaller fishing rod.
What a lovely day. It's so nice to get out of the ocean and work on my tan. I'm so pale.
I've got something. It's putting up a fight.
Seriously? How would you like it if someone hooked you? Give me that.
Ok, I wonder what I'll catch.
This is so exciting. Chef Pierre has a three month waiting list. But I'm here, at last.
Huh? That... that cost an entire month's wage.
I'll go. Please be something nice.
Ah rats. Small. I'm so hungry.
Cool. Eyeballs. They actually look tasty.
Well, let's see what they are like.
I hope it's the big plate.
Yeah! I got it., whoooa whoooa.
It's got to be around here somewhere?
OMG, where did you come from?
I'm not getting a good feeling from this.
It's only food. What's the worst that can happen?
I can't wait to get stuck into this.
No one around... nothing strange... ok.
Who taught you how to eat?
I mean... it was kind of impressive.
I knew she was a big mouth but... wow.
Hey, look at that cute guy over there.
No. Not small again. Not fair.
This is pathetic. How is this a meal?
I need to put glasses on to even see it.
How am I suppose to eat this... I know. Mini noodles need minichopsticks.
This is easy. Who said eating with chopsticks was hard?
I'm getting a warm fuzzy feeling...
I'll try on her ridiculous glasses. Maybe I'll spot something.
Whoa. What are you doing down there?
Wait... I think it's happening again. Help...
Still wearing the glasses. I missed you! Never leave me.
Get off! It's your turn. Go.
Now that is a box of noodles.
I can totally eat all of this.
Got my chopsticks, it's noodle time.
It's nice having a relaxed meal with a friend...
This is so difficult. What card should I go for?
Pizza! My favourite. Look at it.
What? I'll need this later on.
Who needs a a knife and fork... I've got hands.
But I'm sure it'll taste... horrible.
I'm so disappointed. But at least I can eat it.
I'll have a little slice to start.
This is the best thing I've ever tasted.
I love it. Hey, you'll never believe... oh.
...mmm pizza... don't mind if I do..
I baked it myself, especially for you my love.
Please, try a slice. Allow me.
Mmmm. Smells as good as you do.
Open wide, here comes the airplane.
OMG... it melts in my mouth.
Oh look, the last slice... mmmm.
It's mine. I saw it first.
No you didn't. It was me.
Maybe I'll put my hand over here.
If you even... ah... ah... choo.
A brown bag? What's impressive about that?
That's it? Is this a kids meal?
Definitely a tiny burger and fries.
I hope you have a big appetite. ha.
Gee, I wonder whats under here... a burger and fries maybe?
Meh. Ok. I can live with this.
Hmmm, I have a great idea.
I'll just make a little alteration.
It worked! It's the size of my head!
No way! Now this is a super sized meal.
Maybe I can pretend it's a normal burger... what is that noise?
I like salad, but I don't want to wear it.
This is so depressing. Oh well. It's still a burger.
Maybe if I... nice and quiet.
Now this is a happy meal.
